node.text:
One of the most powerful videos I have ever come across. We all experience negative emotions from time to time, but for some it becomes too much. 
.
Today, I wanted to highlight an ongoing issue that we have in this world. Suicide. This video shows you the intimate thoughts a suicidal person has to deal with. More importantly, it shows you that when someone is feeling suicidal the best thing to combat that is love from another human being.
.
Nearly 800,000 people per year commit suicide according to save.org
.
It’s time to bring awareness to this issue, and spread love to those who need it most. Check in on your loved ones. You could be saving their life. #Suicideprevention
.
The gentleman assisting the man in this video is motivational life coach @Tonyrobbins
